<br>
in terms of rangers, how many times have they been the butt of a joke?  they were called mana sponges and weaklings for the longest time.  they didn't get taken seriously until high lvl rangers came around and the epic was introduced, then people started realizing how much dmg they can do.  however, they still can't tank.  i shudder at the thought of a ranger tanking a dragon, although i'd love to have them there to dish the dmg.  a well equipped ranger can get really high ac and attack, but they lack the hps.  <br>
<br>
and rogues, well they were the biggest joke of all back in the day.  they were the class most rarely played pre-kunark and NO ONE wanted them in a group.  after the kunark changes, rogues became the most demanded class because they are some serious dmg dishers.  but they can't tank worth shit.  if you think rangers are poor at taking dmg, rogues are much worse.  they're the little guy that hides behind the mob for a reason.  <br>
<br>
and monks are definately not tanks.  most their gear has barely any ac on it.  most their nice bp's are like 16-20 ac :P.  monks are pullers and can do a nice bit of dmg (although my bf would love to disagree with that dmg).  <br>
<br>
and sk's have gained more respect recently.  the reason they're shown in higher reguard than compared to paladins is cus they have dmg spells that can be casted on any mob (not just undead or stuns :P), that will taunt like mad.  plus they tank pretty well.  they can't do the dmg like a warrior but if you want to center a mob, you just have an sk cast his spells and that mob will be all over him where he wants it to be.  plus they help with pulling in places that monks can't get to.  <br>
<br>
that leaves warriors, the most well-rounded of the bunch.  they can duel wield, which is a HUGE difference in dmg to the paladins and sks, they have the ac, the hp, and the taunting ability.  even if they have matching stats in these areas to a hybrid, they take and do dmg so much better as a whole.  no sane guild would have anyone but a warrior tank major mobs.<br>
<br>
